                            <comment id="15857174" author="jay.zhuang" created="Wed, 8 Feb 2017 01:24:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem is because memtable &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-3.11/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/db/ColumnFamilyStore.java#L410&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;is not initialized for tool&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/cooldoger/cassandra/commit/d2ddeb75cbcbdd407aca33f56f4ab59552a13cdf&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;The fix&lt;/a&gt; is attached.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tjake&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tjake&quot;&gt;tjake&lt;/a&gt; would you please review.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;An alternative fix would be changing &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-3.11/tools/stress/src/org/apache/cassandra/stress/CompactionStress.java#L77&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;toolInitialization()&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-3.11/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/config/DatabaseDescriptor.java#L128&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;daemonInitialization()&lt;/a&gt;. (I prefer the first option, as compaction-stress is really a tool, not daemon).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15960215" author="jay.zhuang" created="Fri, 7 Apr 2017 03:16:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Rebased the code:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&apos;table-wrap&apos;&gt;
&lt;table class=&apos;confluenceTable&apos;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/cooldoger/cassandra/commit/2de68a8ca3d25fa030d8e1a65de68198ea244de2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;3.11&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/cooldoger/cassandra/commit/64912267433c304b1a736df65014f54f177b2e21&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;trunk&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Passed utest locally. Please review.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15960363" author="yukim" created="Fri, 7 Apr 2017 06:43:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It is not initialized because Memtable is tied to commit log, so it creates commit log in commit log directory (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-8616&quot; title=&quot;sstable tools may result in commit log segments be written&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-8616&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-8616&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Option here is to do daemonInitialization in tool.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15961467" author="jay.zhuang" created="Fri, 7 Apr 2017 21:32:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Make sense. Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=yukim&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;yukim&quot;&gt;yukim&lt;/a&gt; for the review. Updated:&lt;/p&gt;
